Package supermarket.domain.controllers

Class DomainController

java.lang.Object
supermarket.domain.controllers.DomainController
public class DomainController extends Object
DomainController class is the main controller of the system. It manages the products, stores, relations between products and the supermarket distributions.

    • getAvailableAlgorithms

      Parameters:
      storeName - Name of the store that contains the shelf.
